Ext.data.JsonP['Appcelerator_Dashboard_Release_Notes']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Appcelerator Dashboard Release Notes</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-43299549\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Appcelerator Dashboard Release Notes</h1>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-43299549_AppceleratorDashboardReleaseNotes-Dashboard4.14.0-29September2017\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Dashboard 4.14.0 - 29 September 2017</span></h2>\n    <p>Dashboard 4.14.0 is a minor release, which includes new features, improvements, and several bug fixes.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-43299549_AppceleratorDashboardReleaseNotes-Newfeatures\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>New features</span></h3>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Dashboard is now available on <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://platform.axway.com\" target=\"_blank\">https://platform.axway.com</a>/ as well as <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://platform.appcelerator.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://platform.appcelerator.com/</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Updated links in the header for Axway University, Developer Portal, and Devlink and Dashboard is now available on the axway.com domains    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Added link in the header for API Central Service    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Added a &quot;Show only my apps&quot; filter to the All Projects page    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Added more application type filters to the All Projects page (Titanium, Native, API Builder, Node.js, and Mobile Backend Services)    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-43299549_AppceleratorDashboardReleaseNotes-Improvements\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Improvements</span></h3>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>An Organization drop-down menu is now available in the header by selecting the Building icon to the right of user&apos;s name    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Replaced activity feed and notification counts in the header with a Bell icon    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Site header now shows user initials instead of a gravatar    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Added password strength meter on the &quot;forgot password&quot; reset form    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Updated the links on the API Management Trial page    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Show version and documentation links in footer when not logged in    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Added an analytics event rate to the organization usage report    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-43299549_AppceleratorDashboardReleaseNotes-Fixedissues\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed issues</span></h3>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Force browser reload when user switches organizations in another tab or window    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Fixed display of small values for cloud storage usage    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Fixed demo data mode toggle (may appear on for users that have previously requested demo mode)    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Fixed intercom control display blocking or interfering with the bottom right portion of some pages    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Fixed the organization drop-down menu in the header to allow access to view expired organizations    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Fixed display of error message on sign-in form when session becomes invalidated or invalid credentials are provided    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Fixed issue when registering new APS SDK applications    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Fixed creating and editing objects in Mobile Backend Services forms    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Fixed issue viewing access and application logs for apps in virtual private cloud environments (VPCs)    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-43299549_AppceleratorDashboardReleaseNotes-RecentReleases\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Recent Releases</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"childpages-macro \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.14.0_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.14.0 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.13.1_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.13.1 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.13.0_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.13.0 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.12.3_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.12.3 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.12.2_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.12.2 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.12.1_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.12.1 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.12.0_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.12.0 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.11.1_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.11.1 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.11.0_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.11.0 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.10.1_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.10.1 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.10.0_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.10.0 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.9.1_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.9.1 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.9.0_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.9.0 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.8.2_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.8.2 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Dashboard_4.8.1_Release_Note\">Dashboard 4.8.1 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>    </p>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=43299549\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Appcelerator Dashboard Release Notes"});